tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Jan 05, 2025</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104mxz1665703028639.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/mxz1665703028639.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/mxz1665703028639.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"mxz1665703028639\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Attachment\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Controls whether the component instance runs in attached mode, meaning that it is created by another component and is deleted when the parent component instance is deleted.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"mxz1665703028639__section_w1265ab1b5b1_w1266ab1b5_w1267ab1\">\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"mxz1665703028639__table_d11036e1_d11037e1_d11038e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"mxz1665703028639__table_d11036e1_d11037e1_d11038e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Value</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"mxz1665703028639__table_d11036e1_d11037e1_d11038e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Description</p>\n</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mxz1665703028639__table_d11036e1_d11037e1_d11038e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">\"\"</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mxz1665703028639__table_d11036e1_d11037e1_d11038e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Not defined.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mxz1665703028639__table_d11036e1_d11037e1_d11038e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">T (Attached)</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mxz1665703028639__table_d11036e1_d11037e1_d11038e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Component instance is attached to another component instance.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mxz1665703028639__table_d11036e1_d11037e1_d11038e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph defvalue\">F (Detached)</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mxz1665703028639__table_d11036e1_d11037e1_d11038e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Component is instance runs in detached mode.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"mxz1665703028639__section_jvj_tsr_4wb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d613015e139\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"mxz1665703028639__p_d97703e1_d97704e1_d97705e1\">If the value is not defined or <code class=\"ph codeph\">false</code>,\n            the value can be overridden by using the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/attached</span> switch in the\n               <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">newinstance</span> ProcScript statement.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"mxz1665703028639__section_itg_5sr_4wb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d613015e157\">Applies To</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"mxz1665703028639__ul_ksm_vsr_4wb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"mxz1665703028639__li_d39623e1_d39624e1_d39625e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"euw1665702582150.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/euw1665702582150.html\" title=\"A Form is a stateful presentation Component that enables users to view and modify data in a Windows or character mode application.\">Form</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"mxz1665703028639__li_d39626e1_d39627e1_d39628e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"rvk1665702582227.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/rvk1665702582227.html\" title=\"A Report is a Component that defines the content and layout of printed output of a Uniface application. It is not interactive and cannot be used to update the database.\">Report</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"mxz1665703028639__li_d39629e1_d39630e1_d39631e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"dww1665702582302.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/dww1665702582302.html\" title=\"A Service is a Component that defines a business logic component, which provides processing that does not require user interaction.\">Service</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"mxz1665703028639__li_d39632e1_d39633e1_d39634e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"uhd1665702582378.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/uhd1665702582378.html\" title=\"A Session Service is a Component that defines a business logic component for handling task-specific data processing for other components.\">Session Service</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"mxz1665703028639__li_d39635e1_d39636e1_d39637e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"mpc1665702582452.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/mpc1665702582452.html\" title=\"An Entity Service is a Component that defines a business logic component that handles database I/O for a single entity on behalf of other components. It is typically used in a generated 3-tier application.\">Entity Service</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ryt1665702577808.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>newinstance</a><p>Creates a new instance of a component.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/srg1705467899529.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Attached Component Instances</a><p>Component instances are said to be attached to the calling component instances when they are created using the /attached switch with the newinstance command, or when the Attach to Parent widget property is set to False.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3614708\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3614708\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Attachment Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Jan 05, 2025 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Attachment Controls whether the component instance runs in attached mode, meaning that it is created by another component and is deleted when the parent component instance is deleted. Value Description \"\" Not defined. T (Attached) Component instance is attached to another component instance. F (Detached) Component is instance runs in detached mode. Description If the value is not defined or false , the value can be overridden by using the /attached switch in the newinstance ProcScript statement. Applies To Form Report Service Session Service Entity Service Related Links newinstance Creates a new instance of a component. Attached Component Instances Component instances are said to be attached to the calling component instances when they are created using the /attached switch with the newinstance command, or when the Attach to Parent widget property is set to False. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}